James Rodriguez believes his permanent future lies at Bayern, despite being on loan from Real Madrid.<br />
<br />
&quot;I think my future is here,&quot; Rodriguez said. &quot;There are a lot of rumors, they talk about a lot of clubs, but right now I&rsquo;m thinking about Bayern Munich. That&rsquo;s my present, and I&rsquo;m happy here.&quot;

